snippet.title: Warhammer Skulls: Tacticus -- Introducing Thousand Sons
snippet.description:
We were delighted to be part of the Warhammer Skulls event on 25 May - and we hope that all the Tacticians who voted for Thousand Sons to be our next faction are equally delighted! #chaos #warhammer40k #mobilegame 

Official merch: https://play.tacticusgame.com/4emMIrE
